{
  "stem": "4710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't get the [NON-ENGLISH], which a Jewish viewer would understand what that means, that we had to have that [NON-ENGLISH], which is a citrus fruit.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think usually that comes from-- either from North Africa or Italy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I suppose during the war years, they were just not available.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only one or two somehow was in the whole country.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people had to go to Budapest if they wanted to keep that commandment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But especially end of-- towards 1943, when the war was not working well to Hungary, when the Russians has counter-offended and there was a lot of Hungarian casualties, and the attitude of the government has changed, it-- one, we felt there came a prime minister who was more friendlier to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we felt that this is now as far as the evil goes and now it's going to be an improvement.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even they were talking about that Horthy doesn't want to give into Hitler.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we really thought, by 1944, that we will survive and the Hungarian Jews will be saved, until it came that fateful day of 19th of March, 1944.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just out of the blue, there was-- it is a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Germans army marched through the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that was a-- one of the main routes towards Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody was very worried that our fate is going to be like the rest of Europe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, there were change of the government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The more-- more balanced politicians has been dismissed and has been appointed right wing politicians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we heard that Horthy, which at that time we looked at him that our savior, the regent [INAUDIBLE] Horthy-- I don't think he was such a great person, such a good person.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
